OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772478695
OL,3,CCrime group leader jokes 'gun
OL,4,Ctrafficking's gone quiet' to detention
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FA leader of an organised crime group
OL,8,Fwho branded himself 'Mr Nobody', while
OL,9,Fplotting to convert more than 150
OL,10,Fblank firearms into live pistols in
OL,11,Fmakeshift gun factories, has been
OL,12,Fjailed.
OL,14,FThe South East Regional Organised
OL,15,FCrime unit raided two properties in
OL,16,FBerkshire where they found more than
OL,17,F150 converted weapons - along with
OL,18,Fhundreds of rounds of converted
OL,19,Fammunition.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
