OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772478695
OL,3,CCrime group leader jokes 'gun
OL,4,Ctrafficking's gone quiet' to detention
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FPaul Lynam, 45, from Waterlooville,
OL,8,FHampshire had fled the UK but was
OL,9,Farrested in Barcelona in August 2024
OL,10,Fand was extradited back in November.
OL,12,FThe police investigation uncovered
OL,13,FLynam played a controlling role,
OL,14,Fcommunicating with the others via a
OL,15,Fcommunications app, using pseudonyms
OL,16,Fincluding Efraim Diveroli, Mr Nobody
OL,17,Fand Pol Pots (sic).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772478695
OL,3,CCrime group leader jokes 'gun
OL,4,Ctrafficking's gone quiet' to detention
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FHe provided postcodes and passwords
OL,8,Ffor deliveries and requested stock
OL,9,Fchecks SEROCU officers also found
OL,10,Fevidence of cash being transferred to
OL,11,FLynam.
OL,13,FPaul Lynam, of Hannah Gardens,
OL,14,FWaterlooville, Hampshire, appeared at
OL,15,FPortsmouth Crown Court where he was
OL,16,Fsentenced on Friday (27 February) to
OL,17,F16 years and six months' imprisonment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
