FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772478695
OL,3,CCrime group leader jokes 'gun
OL,4,Ctrafficking's gone quiet' to detention
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FLynam appeared at the same court on 6
OL,8,FMarch 2025 where he pleaded guilty to
OL,9,Ftwo counts of conspiracy to sell or
OL,10,Ftransfer prohibited weapons, two
OL,11,Fcounts of conspiracy to sell or
OL,12,Ftransfer ammunition and money
OL,13,Flaundering.
OL,15,FFive other members of the organised
OL,16,Fcrime group have already been
OL,17,Fsentenced for their roles.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
