FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772478695
OL,3,CCrime group leader jokes 'gun
OL,4,Ctrafficking's gone quiet' to detention
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FDamon Denham, then aged 36, of Common
OL,8,FRoad, Slough was sentenced to 13 years
OL,9,Fand one month imprisonment at a
OL,10,Fhearing at Reading Crown Court on 1
OL,11,FMarch 2024. Two other men were also
OL,12,Fsentenced at this hearing.
OL,14,FChad Blackwell, then aged 34, of
OL,15,FHensworth Road, Ashford, Surrey was
OL,16,Fsentenced to 11 years and three
OL,17,Fmonths' imprisonment.
OL,19,FDaniel Boyd, then aged 42, of Talbot
OL,20,FPlace, Datchet, was sentenced to eight
OL,21,Fyears and three months' imprisonment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
