PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772478695
OL,3,CCrime group leader jokes 'gun
OL,4,Ctrafficking's gone quiet' to detention
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FAll three men pleaded guilty at
OL,8,Fprevious hearings to, conspiracy to
OL,9,Fsell/transfer prohibited weapons and
OL,10,Fconspiracy to sell/transfer prohibited
OL,11,Fammunition. Boyd also pleaded guilty
OL,12,Fto having an offensive weapon.
OL,14,FOn 7 June 2024, at Portsmouth Crown
OL,15,FCourt two other men were sentenced.
OL,17,FPerry Binns, then aged 37, of
OL,18,FWesterham Close, Cosham was sentenced
OL,19,Fto eight years' imprisonment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
