PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772478695
OL,3,CCrime group leader jokes 'gun
OL,4,Ctrafficking's gone quiet' to detention
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FHe previously pleaded guilty to one
OL,8,Fcount of conspiracy to sell/transfer
OL,9,Ffirearms, one count of conspiracy to
OL,10,Fsell/transfer ammunition and one count
OL,11,Fof possession with intent to supply
OL,12,Fheroin.
OL,14,FSteve Jones, then aged 46, of Fratton
OL,15,FRoad, Portsmouth was sentenced to 10
OL,16,Fyears' imprisonment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
