PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772478695
OL,3,CCrime group leader jokes 'gun
OL,4,Ctrafficking's gone quiet' to detention
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FOn 22 February 2024, warrants were
OL,8,Fcarried out in Westerham Close,
OL,9,FCosham, and Mays Yard industrial
OL,10,Festate, Horndean, which turned up more
OL,11,Fthan 70 converted firearms, there were
OL,12,Fmore in various stages of being
OL,13,Fconverted, and more 600 rounds of
OL,14,Fammunition that had been hidden in
OL,15,Fsuitcases.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772478695
OL,3,CCrime group leader jokes 'gun
OL,4,Ctrafficking's gone quiet' to detention
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FSenior investigating officer Det Ch
OL,8,FInsp Clair Trueman said: "Lynam's role
OL,9,Fin leading an organised crime group,
OL,10,Fwhich converted blank firearms into
OL,11,Flive pistols at various locations,
OL,12,Fposed a lethal threat our communities
OL,13,Facross the south east.
OL,15,F"He, along with Denham, Blackwell,
OL,16,FBoyd, Binns and Jones, showed complete
OL,17,Fdisregard for the danger these weapons
OL,18,Fpresented.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
