OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772478695
OL,3,CCrime group leader jokes 'gun
OL,4,Ctrafficking's gone quiet' to detention
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,F"Their only consideration was
OL,8,Fprofiting from others' misery when
OL,9,Fundoubtedly, the weapons would have
OL,10,Fbeen used for criminal activities.
OL,12,F"We continue to make every effort to
OL,13,Ftackle the threat of firearms and
OL,14,Fdisrupt serious and organised crime in
OL,15,Four communities and beyond."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
